{"blogid": "124079629", "writerAge": "码龄3年", "writerBlogNum": "1", "writerCollect": "10", "writerComment": "0", "writerFan": "0", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "10", "writerName": "n1ght、", "writerProfileAdress": "..\\..\\static\\writer_image\\profile_124079629.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "248613", "writerRankWeekly": "1288040", "writerThumb": "0", "writerVisitNum": "2041", "blog_read_count": "2040", "blog_time": "已于 2022-05-06 00:23:42 修改", "blog_title": "LAMP环境搭建", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"../../static/bootstrap/css/csdnstyle.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"htmledit_views\" id=\"content_views\">\n<p id=\"%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9C%A8%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9C%A8%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\">一、在虚拟机上安装Linux系统</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\">二、安装Apache</a></p>\n<p id=\"1.%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%BA%93-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#1.%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%BA%93\">1.下载好后，看了看版本，不是太老，就没有继续安装。</a></p>\n<p id=\"2.%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFApache%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#2.%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFApache%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\">2.开启Apache服务</a></p>\n<p id=\"3.%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEApache%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#3.%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEApache%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\">3.设置Apache开机启动服务</a></p>\n<p id=\"4.%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BAIP%EF%BC%89-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#4.%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BAIP%EF%BC%89\">4.尝试一下是否启动了服务（访问虚拟机IP）</a></p>\n<p id=\"%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql\">三、安装mysql</a></p>\n<p id=\"1.%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDmysql%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#1.%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDmysql%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85\">1.下载mysql安装包</a></p>\n<p id=\"2.%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql%E5%8C%85-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#2.%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql%E5%8C%85\">2.安装mysql包</a></p>\n<p id=\"3.%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%20%2Fetc%2Fyum.repos.d%2F%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%89-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#3.%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%20%2Fetc%2Fyum.repos.d%2F%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%89\">3.安装mysql服务（打开 /etc/yum.repos.d/后再执行）</a></p>\n<p id=\"4.%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8mysql%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#4.%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8mysql%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\">4.启动mysql服务</a></p>\n<p id=\"5.%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95mql-toc\" style=\"margin-left:40px;\"><a href=\"#5.%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95mql\">5.登录mql</a></p>\n<p id=\"%C2%A0%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PHP-toc\" style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"#%C2%A0%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PHP\"> 四、安装PHP</a></p>\n<hr/>\n<h1 id=\"%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\"><a id=\"_7\"></a>前言</h1>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">       针对LAMP环境，之前只是在服务器上尝试过一键搭建。借此次机会，尝试下手动搭建LAMP环境。</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\">     LAMP，顾名思义是搭建Linux+Apache+mysql+php。即以Linux系统为基础，在其上搭建Apache、mysql、php来使系统可以运行PHP脚本文件。</p>\n<hr/>\n<h1 id=\"%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E5%9C%A8%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Linux%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F\">一、在虚拟机上安装Linux系统</h1>\n<p>      对此不再赘述，网上资源一抓一大把，按照步骤安装Linux系统即可。本次使用的是centos7（本来纠结linux版本是用CentOS还是Ubuntu，之前觉着都差不多，但去看了下资料，centos做服务器更加稳定的，所以决定用centos试试）。</p>\n<p>     <img alt=\"\" height=\"294\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\672f150732684bed8dbd2cca216e026f.png\" width=\"495\"/></p>\n<p>    安装成功！</p>\n<p></p>\n<h1 id=\"%E4%BA%8C%E3%80%81%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\">二、安装Apache</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1.%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E5%BA%93\">1.下载好后，看了看版本，不是太老，就没有继续安装。</h2>\n<pre><code>yum -y install httpd</code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">     <img alt=\"\" height=\"254\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\01130b4938c54e16bccd25ff87858d16.png\" width=\"565\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"2.%E5%BC%80%E5%90%AFApache%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" style=\"text-align:left;\">2.开启Apache服务</h2>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">    <img alt=\"\" height=\"41\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\3fd8e5521043463b8fd58ba4bb07b82e.png\" width=\"374\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"3.%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AEApache%E5%BC%80%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" style=\"text-align:left;\">3.设置Apache开机启动服务</h2>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">    <img alt=\"\" height=\"73\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\f3377218c61d41eeb56d32d981e1017c.png\" width=\"618\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"4.%E5%B0%9D%E8%AF%95%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%8B%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E4%BA%86%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E8%AE%BF%E9%97%AE%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BAIP%EF%BC%89\" style=\"text-align:left;\">4.尝试一下是否启动了服务（访问虚拟机IP）</h2>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">     <img alt=\"\" height=\"235\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\13b2170f7e6e4b4e9ef3d4924787522b.png\" width=\"550\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">      成功！</p>\n<h1 id=\"%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql\" style=\"text-align:left;\">三、安装mysql</h1>\n<h2 id=\"1.%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BDmysql%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8C%85\" style=\"text-align:left;\">1.下载mysql安装包</h2>\n<pre><code>wget http://repo.mysql.com/mysql57-community-release-el7-10.noarch.rpm</code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">   <img alt=\"\" height=\"266\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\0d2b3d296bd447c3973b2dd88df547e3.png\" width=\"469\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"2.%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql%E5%8C%85\" style=\"text-align:left;\">2.安装mysql包</h2>\n<pre><code>rpm -ivh mysql57-community-release-el7-8.noarch.rpm</code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">   <img alt=\"\" height=\"61\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\33f25429433046b78bb430a86b5c632d.png\" width=\"516\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"3.%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85mysql%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%EF%BC%88%E6%89%93%E5%BC%80%20%2Fetc%2Fyum.repos.d%2F%E5%90%8E%E5%86%8D%E6%89%A7%E8%A1%8C%EF%BC%89\" style=\"text-align:left;\">3.安装mysql服务<code>（打开 /etc/yum.repos.d/后再执行）</code></h2>\n<pre><code>yum -y install mysql-server</code></pre>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">  <img alt=\"\" height=\"169\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\04d9823941064cef89c0628265cc90b7.png\" width=\"568\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">   <img alt=\"\" height=\"66\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\14df59705c64437b91ac451afabf9e6c.png\" width=\"573\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">  失败后，找到修复方法：修改mysql-community.repo文件（该文件就在<code>yum.repos.d里</code>）将里面的gpgcheck=1修改为  gpgcheck=0，成功安装！！</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\">   <img alt=\"\" height=\"245\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\f4932ebf16e04adbaa07945963883d58.png\" width=\"408\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"4.%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8mysql%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\" style=\"text-align:left;\">4.启动mysql服务</h2>\n<pre><code>systemctl start mysqld\n</code></pre>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">    <img alt=\"\" height=\"39\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\39d27c63ad0e4a50a0ecdd088a42d3c1.png\" width=\"352\"/></p>\n<h2 id=\"5.%E7%99%BB%E5%BD%95mql\" style=\"text-align:left;\">5.登录mql</h2>\n<pre><code>mysql -u root -p\n</code></pre>\n<p>    <img alt=\"\" height=\"249\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\7d13a4dd465a481b8ec89dc62e953b56.png\" width=\"596\"/></p>\n<p>    成功！</p>\n<h1 id=\"%C2%A0%E5%9B%9B%E3%80%81%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85PHP\"> 四、安装PHP</h1>\n<p>    <img alt=\"\" height=\"275\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\3fc759121c2f463c819ebe142a90d315.png\" width=\"586\"/></p>\n<p>    <img alt=\"\" height=\"200\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\2bb677fc6b98478bbb53d8b0984b7daf.png\" width=\"534\"/></p>\n<p>yum直接安装都是php5，想安装PHP7，一定要先升级yum！！！</p>\n<p><a class=\"link-info\" href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/u010433704/article/details/105306465?ops_request_misc=%257B%2522request%255Fid%2522%253A%2522164863504916782246426184%2522%252C%2522scm%2522%253A%252220140713.130102334..%2522%257D&amp;request_id=164863504916782246426184&amp;biz_id=0&amp;utm_medium=distribute.pc_search_result.none-task-blog-2~all~baidu_landing_v2~default-3-105306465.142%5Ev5%5Epc_search_insert_es_download,143%5Ev6%5Econtrol&amp;utm_term=CentOS7+%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85php7&amp;spm=1018.2226.3001.4187\" title=\"PHP5不用删除，直接安装PHP7办法\">PHP5不用删除，直接安装PHP7办法</a></p>\n<p>   <img alt=\"\" height=\"96\" src=\"..\\..\\static\\image\\ce074ca6c83a4218b00882e0d77bf4d6.png\" width=\"626\"/></p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:justify;\">PHP7安装成功！</p>\n<p style=\"margin-left:.0001pt;text-align:left;\"><strong><strong>至此，LAMP环境搭建完成！</strong></strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>", "first_tag": "PHP", "cpp": 0, "csharp": 0, "python": 0, "javascript": 0, "java": 0, "sql": 1, "php": 1, "time": "2022-05-06 00:23:42", "summary": "前言一、在虚拟机上安装系统二、安装下载好后，看了看版本，不是太老，就没有继续安装。开启服务设置开机启动服务尝试一下是否启动了服务访问虚拟机三、安装下载安装包安装包安装服务打开后再执行启动服务登录四、安"}